data.description: Welcome to this inviting 3-bedroom plus den, 2-bathroom house in Lehigh Acres, now available for sale. Inside, you'll find an open concept design with tile flooring throughout for easy maintenance. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances and offers a seamless flow to the screened-in lanai, which overlooks the fenced backyard, perfect for relaxation or play. Additionally, this home features charming French doors, adding character to the living space. Plus, it includes a hot tub for your enjoyment. Conveniently located, this home is just a short drive from shopping, the Forum, and I-75, making daily life a breeze. Don't miss out on this opportunity to call it your own!!
